name: Sunset on a Beach - Camera Roll #1
description:
I remember this was one of the first picture I've captured with a camera, real camera. I remember how I dialed the knob, figuring out the best setting for every scenario. It's thrilling, to finally able to experience a real camera in your hand for the first time.

Since it's one of my first picture I've captured, I think it deserved the place as the first NFT I created. It also will be my stepping stone as I embark to this new realm.
